King [[chemistry]], ing '''molecule''' metung yang [[electric charge|electrically]] neutral a grupu da reng e kukulang kareng aduang [[atom]] a maki ustung tatag (''sufficiently stable'') king partikular a pangaayus a pibubuklud da reng aduang tutung masikan a [[chemical bond]]. Maliari ya muring mangabaldugan a unit da reng adua o maigit pang atom a pibubuklud da reng covalent bond.<ref name="iupac">{{GoldBookRef|title=molecule|url=http://goldbook.iupac.org/M04002.html|year=1994}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Pauling, Linus |title=General Chemistry|location=New York | publisher=Dover Publications, Inc.|year=1970|id=ISBN 0-486-65622-5}}<br> {{cite book| author=Ebbin, Darrell, D. |title=General Chemistry, 3th Ed.|location=Boston | publisher=Houghton Mifflin Co.|year=1990|id=ISBN 0-395-43302-9}}<br>{{cite book|author=Brown, T.L. |title=Chemistry - the Central Science, 9th Ed.|location=New Jersey | publisher=Prentice Hall|year=2003|id=ISBN 0-13-066997-0}}<br>{{cite book|author=Chang, Raymond |title=Chemistry, 6th Ed.|location=New York | publisher=McGraw Hill|year=1998|id=ISBN 0-07-115221-0}}<br>{{cite book|author=Zumdahl, Steven S. |title= Chemistry, 4th ed.|location= Boston |publisher= Houghton Mifflin|year= 1997|id=ISBN 0-669-41794-7}}</ref> King [[organic chemistry]] ampong [[biochemistry]], e makanian kaigpit ing pamangamit king katayang ''molecule,'' at magagamit ya murin iti kareng charged a [[organic compound|organic molecule]] ampong [[biomolecule]].
Makikilala la reng molecule kareng [[polyatomic ion]] king maigpit a kabaldugan a iti.

Linto ya ing kabaldugan a iti aniang miragdagan ing beluan tungkul king pangabalangkas (''structure'') da reng molecule. E la makaing eksaktu deng minunang kabaldugan kareng molecule antimong pekamalating [[w:list of particles#Molecules|lkapirasu]] (particle) ning purung sangkap a chemical (''chemical substance'') nung nu atiu pa murin ing komposisiun ampong kaurian a chemical.<ref>[http://antoine.frostburg.edu/chem/senese/101/glossary/m.shtml#molecule Molecule Definition]  (Frostburg State University)</ref> Maralas mikakaprublema king kabaldugan a iti, uling king aldo-aldong bie, dakal la reng sangkap (substance), antimo deng batu (rocks), asin (salts), ampong metal, bibilugan da lang atom o [[ion]], oneng e la gawa kareng molecule.  

King [[kinetic theory]] da reng [[gas]]es, ing katayang ''molecule'' maralas yang magagamit king sanumang butil a gas, nanu man ing kayang sangkap o komposisiun.<ref>E.g. see [http://www.usd.edu/phys/courses/phys_111sf/ch_10/10_notes.htm]</ref> Agpang king kabaldugan a iti, tuturing da la mu namang ''molecule'' deng  [[noble gas]]es, lipat ning bibilugan no ning metung a atom a alang bond.

